  "title": "Patient Service Associate (Office Hours / 5 Days / Immediate Start) #HJG",
  "description": "<h3>Job Responsibilities:</h3><ul><li>Assist patients with appointment scheduling and registration</li><li>Handle patient enquiries in person, over the phone, and via email</li><li>Manage patient records and ensure accuracy of data entry</li><li>Support administrative tasks related to patient care and clinic operations</li><li>Coordinate with healthcare professionals to facilitate smooth patient flow</li><li>Provide assistance with billing and insurance documentation</li></ul><h3>Job Requirements:</h3><ul><li>Minimum GCE ‘N’ Level or ‘O’ Level / Diploma and above</li><li>No experience needed; full training will be provided</li><li>Basic knowledge of Microsoft Office</li><li>Able to start work immediately</li></ul><p>If you are interested in this position, do kindly drop your most updated resume to joshua.gan@recruitexpress.com.sg and leonleong@recruitexpress.com.sg (Attn: Patient Service Associate)</p><p>Leon Leong De Cong<br />R1551708<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifesciences Division)<br />EA License: 99C4599</p>",
